doc.after: Kentucky can be divided into five primary regions the Cumberland Plateau in the east the north central Bluegrass region the south central and western Pennyroyal Plateau also known as the Pennyrile or Mississippi Plateau the Western Coal Fields and the far west Jackson Purchase
